# <%= appName %> — Hexagonal Architecture (Ports & Adapters)

The **core** is isolated from delivery mechanisms and infrastructure. Adapters plug into ports.

## Structure

```
src/
  core/
    domain/           # entities, value objects
    application/      # services use cases
    ports/
      inbound/        # driven by HTTP, CLI, queues
      outbound/       # drive DB, APIs, messaging
  adapters/
    inbound/http/     # <%= backend %> routes
    outbound/persistence/
  wiring/             # DI container
```

Inbound adapters call inbound ports. Outbound adapters implement outbound ports.
